Some pranks you can play on your Uber driver include: 
- Asking them to find a nearby restaurant and then giving them a fake address; 
- Slightly altering your voice so that they can't understand you, and telling them to turn in a different direction; 
- Making up an imaginary destination and seeing if they try to take you there; 
- Asking them to pick you up at an impossible-to-find location or far away from your actual drop-off address.
